data.remarks: The name of Company has been changed to Jubilant Consumer Pvt. Ltd.

Jubilant Enpro Services Limited ("JESPL"), in one of the promoter company holding 32,022,947 equity shares (i.e. amounting 48.70% of the total paid-up capital).Further, Alllahabad High Court vide its order dated November 19, 2015 approved the composite scheme of arrangement between Jubilant Enpro Services Private Limited ("JESPL"), JSPL Consultants & Management Services Pvt. Ltd. ("JSPL") and Jubilant Fresh Private Limited ("JFPL"). Pursuant to the High Court order, 32,022,947 equity shares of the company held by JESPL have been transferred from JESPL to JFPL. The said order has been made effective from January 11, 2016. Also, in terms of the order JESPL stands dissolved from effective date.
